com.betabot.script.wrappers

Class RSComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betabot.script.api.MethodProvider
      • com.betabot.script.wrappers.RSComponent

  • public class RSComponent
extends MethodProvider
    Represents an interface component. An RSComponent may or may not have a parent component, and will always have a parent RSInterface.
    Author:
    Qauters, Jacmob
